lpha1/` with proper package structure, scheme registration, and CRD markers for controller-gen.\\n14: \\n15: #### Scenario: Package structure exists\\n16: - **GIVEN** the repository root at `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube`\\n17: - **WHEN** examining `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/`\\n18: - **THEN** the directory SHALL contain:\\n19:   - `doc.go` with `+k8s:deepcopy-gen=package` marker\\n20:   - `register.go` with `SchemeGroupVersion` set to `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1`\\n21:   - `codeinterpreter_types.go` with `CodeInterpreter` and `CodeInterpreterList` types\\n22:   - `shared_types.go` with `AuthModeType` enum and `TargetPort` type\\n23:   - `zz_generated.deepcopy.go` (generated)\\n24: \\n25: #### Scenario: Scheme group version is correct\\n26: - **GIVEN** `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/groupversion_info.go`\\n27: - **WHEN** reading the file\\n28: - **THEN** `GroupVersion` SHALL be `schema.GroupVersion{Group: \\\"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh\\\", Version: \\\"v1alpha1\\\"}`\\n29: \\n30...\n  Line 14: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775840463022,\"sessionID\":\"ses_287a93498ffeFhL5U8XVgdSX8y\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d78570864001svtf7QB7Z7F05a\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d7856e4be001hHSEl3GvglxLVE\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_287a93498ffeFhL5U8XVgdSX8y\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"read\",\"callID\":\"toolu_tool-f88f71c446fe4260aabfdc2e67d1f59b\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-001/proposal.md\"},\"output\":\"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-001/proposal.md</path>\\n<type>file</type>\\n<content>\\n1: # AR-001 — CRD AgentRuntime 类型定义 Proposal\\n2: \\n3: ## Purpose\\n4: \\n5: Define the foundational Go type structures for `AgentRuntime` and `CodeInterpreter` CRDs in the `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1` package. These types serve as the core data model for AgentCube's sandbox orchestration platform, enabling:\\n6: \\n7: 1. **Sandbox Template Definition**: Users define pod templates and runtime parameters via CRDs\\n8: 2. **Controller Integration**: The workload manager controller uses these types to create/manage `Sandbox` and `SandboxClaim` resources\\n9: 3. **Client Generation**: These types are the source for `k8s.io/code-generator` to produce typed clients, informers, and listers (see `deployment/client-go.md`)\\n10: 4. **Helm Chart CRDs**: `controller-gen` generates CRD YAML from these types (see `manifests/charts/base/crds/`)\\n11: \\n12: ## Scope\\n13: \\n14: ### In Scope\\n15: \\n16: | Deliverable | Description |\\n17: |-------------|-------------|\\n18: | `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/types.go` | Type definitions for AgentRuntime, CodeInterpreter, TargetPort, and related structs |\\n19: | `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/doc.go` | Package documentation with boilerplate |\\n20: | `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/register.go` | Scheme registration for `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1` |\\n21: \\n22: ### Type Definitions Required\\n23: \\n24: #### Age...\n  Line 15: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775840463024,\"sessionID\":\"ses_287a93498ffeFhL5U8XVgdSX8y\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d7856f4a7001rNpT3GXbLQ2VQG\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d7856e4be001hHSEl3GvglxLVE\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_287a93498ffeFhL5U8XVgdSX8y\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"read\",\"callID\":\"toolu_tool-46bbfd00f78a49bfb40bc9ed058841fc\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-002/proposal.md\"},\"output\":\"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-002/proposal.md</path>\\n<type>file</type>\\n<content>\\n1: # AR-002 — CRD CodeInterpreter 类型定义 Proposal\\n2: \\n3: ## Purpose\\n4: \\n5: Define the Go type structures for `CodeInterpreter` CRD in the `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1` package. This CRD provides a specialized sandbox runtime for code execution environments with enhanced features:\\n6: \\n7: 1. **Warm Pool Management**: Pre-provisioned sandboxes for low-latency startup\\n8: 2. **Authentication Integration**: Support for picod auth mode\\n9: 3. **Port Exposure**: HTTP/HTTPS endpoints for code interpreter communication\\n10: 4. **Resource Management**: CPU/Memory limits for code execution sandboxes\\n11: \\n12: ## Scope\\n13: \\n14: ### In Scope\\n15: \\n16: | Deliverable | Description |\\n17: |-------------|-------------|\\n18: | `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/codeinterpreter_types.go` | Type definitions for CodeInterpreter, CodeInterpreterSpec, CodeInterpreterStatus, CodeInterpreterList |\\n19: | Supporting types | CodeInterpreterSandboxTemplate, AuthModeType constants, validation markers |\\n20: \\n21: ### Type Definitions Required\\n22: \\n23: #### CodeInterpreter\\n24: \\n25: ```\\n26: CodeInterpreter\\n27: ├── Spec\\n28: │   ├── Ports ([]TargetPort, JSON: ports)\\n29: │   ├── Template (*CodeInterpreterSandboxTemplate, JSON: template, required)\\n30: │   ├── SessionTimeout (*metav1.Duration, default: 15m)\\n31: │   ├── MaxSessionDuration (*metav1.Durat...\n  Line 19: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775840480496,\"sessionID\":\"ses_287a93498ffeFhL5U8XVgdSX8y\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d7857458f001fN8mmH0kGM3AaV\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d78570903001sLoaOwLuJlAFqY\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_287a93498ffeFhL5U8XVgdSX8y\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"read\",\"callID\":\"toolu_tool-3f14e7a04c45459fa07009c1b8116cc0\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-001/spec.md\"},\"output\":\"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-001/spec.md</path>\\n<type>file</type>\\n<content>\\n1: # AR-001 — CRD AgentRuntime 类型定义\\n2: \\n3: ## Metadata\\n4: \\n5: | Item | Value |