le\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/proposal.md\",\"before\":\"# AR-001 — CRD AgentRuntime 类型定义\\n\\n## Purpose\\n\\nDefine the `AgentRuntime` Custom Resource Definition (CRD) types in `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1` to enable Kubernetes-native sandbox orches...\n  Line 38: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775840308288,\"sessionID\":\"ses_287adca13ffeZMR47Fm5As7vW1\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d78533f41001xP3bLGFimBsraS\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d78532dfe001slHi5ey1wAbQdm\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_287adca13ffeZMR47Fm5As7vW1\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"edit\",\"callID\":\"toolu_functions.edit:15\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/proposal.md\",\"newString\":\"# Validate CRD schema\\nkubectl apply -f manifests/charts/base/crds/ --dry-run=server\\n```\\n\\n---\\n\\n# AR-002 — CRD CodeInterpreter 类型定义\\n\\n## Purpose\\n\\nDefine the `CodeInterpreter` Custom Resource Definition (CRD) types in `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1` to enable Kubernetes-native code execution environments for AI agents. The CodeInterpreter CRD represents a specialized sandbox instance designed for executing code snippets safely. This work extends the existing `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1` API group with the `CodeInterpreter` type alongside `AgentRuntime`, sharing the same scheme registration and code generation pipeline.\\n\\n## Scope\\n\\n### In scope\\n\\n| Item | Detail |\\n|------|--------|\\n| **Package** | `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1` |\\n| **API group** | `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh` |\\n| **Version** | `v1alpha1` |\\n| **Types defined** | `CodeInterpreter`, `CodeInterpreterList`, `CodeInterpreterSpec`, `CodeInterpreterStatus`, `CodeInterpreterPhase` |\\n| **Scheme registration** | Update `register.go` to include `CodeInterpreter` and `CodeInterpreterList` in `addKnownTypes` |\\n| **Kubebuilder markers** | `+genclient`, `+k8s:deepcopy-gen`, `+kubebuilder:object:root=true`, `+kubebuilder:subresource:status`, `+kubebuilder:resource:scope=Namespaced`, `+kubebuilder:printcolumn`, validation markers |\\n| **Code generation** | `controller-gen crd` → `manifests/charts/base/crds/`; `controller-gen object` → `zz_generated.deepcopy.go`; `k8s.io/code-generator` → `client-go/` |\\n| **Gen...\n  Line 41: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775840355341,\"sessionID\":\"ses_287adca13ffeZMR47Fm5As7vW1\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d78554d7b001syoZ0fVbY7pgZY\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d7854ac74001dJ51vpHuAZW6mY\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_287adca13ffeZMR47Fm5As7vW1\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"read\",\"callID\":\"toolu_functions.read:16\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/proposal.md\",\"offset\":1,\"limit\":60},\"output\":\"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/proposal.md</path>\\n<type>file</type>\\n<content>\\n1: # AgentCube CRD Type Definitions\\n2: \\n3: This proposal defines the Custom Resource Definition (CRD) types for the AgentCube project.\\n4: \\n5: ---\\n6: \\n7: # AR-001 — CRD AgentRuntime 类型定义\\n8: \\n9: ## Purpose\\n10: \\n11: Define the `AgentRuntime` Custom Resource Definition (CRD) types in `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1` to enable Kubernetes-native sandbox orchestration for AI agent workloads. This work establishes the core API surface — `AgentRuntime`, `AgentRuntimeSpec`, `AgentRuntimeStatus`, and supporting shared types — that the Workload Manager controller and generated `client-go` library consume.\\n12: \\n13: ## Scope\\n14: \\n15: ### In scope\\n16: \\n17: | Item | Detail |\\n18: |------|--------|\\n19: | **Package** | `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1` |\\n20: | **API group** | `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh` |\\n21: | **Version** | `v1alpha1` |\\n22: | **Types defined** | `AgentRuntime`, `AgentRuntimeList`, `AgentRuntimeSpec`, `AgentRuntimeStatus`, `TargetPort`, `ProtocolType`, `SandboxTemplate` |\\n23: | **Scheme registration** | `groupversion_info.go`, `register.go` — `GroupVersion`, `SchemeBuilder`, `AddToScheme`, kind constants, `Resource()` helper |\\n24: | **Kubebuilder markers** | `+genclient`, `+k8s:deepcopy-gen`, `+kubebuilder:object:root=true`, `+kubebuilder:subresource:status`, `+kubebuilder:resource:scope=Namespaced`,...\n  Line 44: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775840388220,\"sessionID\":\"ses_287adca13ffeZMR47Fm5As7vW1\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d78558273001rfNjf2qTIZxbqh\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d78556440001C4pmvx6a216kAv\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_287adca13ffeZMR47Fm5As7vW1\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"read\",\"callID\":\"toolu_functions.read:17\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/proposal.md\",\"limit\":60,\"offset\":480},\"output\":\"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/proposal.md</path>\\n<type>file</type>\\n<content>\\n480: | Fake clients | `client-go/.../fake/` test doubles for unit testing |\\n481: \\n482: ### Breaking change risk\\n483: \\n484: - **Low**: This is a greenfield type definition that extends the existing API group. No existing runtime behavior is modified.\\n485: - **Compatibility**: Shares the same `v1alpha1` version with `AgentRuntime`, ensuring consistent scheme registration and versioning.\\n486: - **Future**: Adding required fields to `CodeInterpreterSpec` after initial release will require CRD version bump and conversion webhook.\\n487: \\n488: ## Alternatives considered\\n489: \\n490: ### 1. Extend AgentRuntime instead of separate CRD\\n491: \\n492: **Approach**: Add a `codeExecution` field to `AgentRuntimeSpec` to support code interpreter use cases within the existing AgentRuntime CRD.\\n493: \\n494: **Rejected because**: CodeInterpreter has distinct lifecycle semantics and configuration requirements (timeout, memory limits) compared to general agent runtimes. Separate CRDs allow independent RBAC, scheduling, and lifecycle management. The client-go library pattern (see spec) explicitly defines separate interfaces for `AgentRuntimes` and `CodeInterpreters`, indicating intentional separation.\\n495: \\n496: ### 2. Use v1beta1 version for CodeInterpreter\\n497: \\n498: **Approach**: Define CodeInterpreter in a new API version `v1beta1` while keeping Agen...\n  Line 50: {\"type\":\"text\",\"timestamp\":1775840415468,\"sessionID\":\"ses_287adca13ffeZMR47Fm5As7vW1\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d78563032001o4ZTQRg8v84JMk\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d7856127e001TFVzl5igyOfUSd\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_287adca13ffeZMR47Fm5As7vW1\",\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Done. I've updated `proposal.md` with the AR-002 section for **CodeInterpreter CRD Type Definition**.\\n\\n## Summary of Changes\\n\\nThe proposal now contains two main sections:\\n\\n### AR-001 — CRD AgentRuntime 类型定义 (Existing)\\nThe original AgentRuntime CRD proposal with all its details preserved.\\n\\n### AR-002 — CRD CodeInterpreter 类型定义 (New)\\nAdded a comprehensive proposal section covering:\\n\\n- **Purpose**: Defines CodeInterpreter CRD for Kubernetes-native code execution environments\\n- **Scope**: In-scope items (types, scheme registration, code generation) and out-of-scope items\\n- **Design**: File layout, type definitions including:\\n  - `CodeInterpreterPhase` enum (Pending/Running/Succeeded/Failed)\\n  - `CodeInterpreter` root CRD with kubebuilder markers\\n  - `CodeInterpreterSpec` (Image, Resources, Env, TimeoutSeconds, MaxMemoryMB)\\n  - `CodeInterpreterStatus` (Phase, Conditions, SandboxID, ExecutionCount, etc.)\\n  - `CodeInterpreterList`\\n  - Scheme registration updates to `register.go`\\n  - Code generation pipeline\\n- **Impact Analysis**: Files created/modified/generated, downstream consumers, breaking change risk\\n- **Alternatives Considered**:\\n  1. Extend AgentRuntime vs separate CRD (rejected - distinct lifecycle semantics)\\n  2. Use v1beta1 version (rejected - unnecessary complexity)\\n  3. Embed full PodSpec (rejected - controlled API surface preferred)\\n  4. Separate API group (rejected - shared runtime concerns)\\n- **Dependencies**: Same as AR-001 (k8s.io/apimachinery, k8s.io/api, controller-runtime, etc.)\\n- **Verification**: Build, test, and validation commands\",\"time\":{\"start\":1775840415466,\"end\":1775840415466}}}\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/results/runs/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z_logs/AR-002_ST-4.log:\n  Line 14: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775840293314,\"sessionID\":\"ses_287abc318ffel7tpmE2F2RUOxc\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d78547077001CV01AdvekGUSvS\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d78545c32001D7HcyUNdqFYj82\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_287abc318ffel7tpmE2F2RUOxc\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"bash\",\"callID\":\"toolu_tool-4cad3de26dfc489185765c94be2b30b8\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"command\":\"find /home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z -name \\\"*AR-*\\\" -o -name \\\"*ar-*\\\" -o -name \\\"*codeinterpreter*\\\" -o -name \\\"*CodeInterpreter*\\\" 2>/dev/null | head -20\",\"description\":\"Find AR or CodeInterpreter related files\"},\"output\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/sandbox-orchestration/AR-005-sandbox-creation-processor\\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-002\\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-001\\n\",\"metadata\":{\"output\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/sandbox-orchestration/AR-005-sandbox-creation-processor\\n/home/