tworkPolicy`, and lifecycle hooks across multiple CRDs\\n2. **Establish naming conventions** - Consistent naming for phases, conditions, and resource types\\n3. **Provide reusable validation utilities** - Shared validation functions for common fields\\n4. **Enable code generation consistency** - Ensure generated client-go code follows consistent patterns\\n\\n## Scope\\n\\n**Module:** `pkg/apis`  \\n**Language:** Go  \\n**Size:** S\\n\\nThis AR covers:\\n\\n- **In scope:**\\n  - Common type definitions in `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/types.go`\\n  - Constant definitions for phases and condition types\\n  - Shared validation utilities\\n  - Documentation of patterns for future CRDs\\n\\n- **Out of scope:**\\n  - Changes to existing CRD structures (AgentRuntime, CodeInterpreter)\\n  - Client-go code generation changes\\n  - Controller logic modifications\\n\\n## Current State Analysis\\n\\n### Existing Shared Types\\n\\nThe codebase already has several types that could be considered \\\"shared\\\":\\n\\n1. **`ResourceQuota`** (`types.go:80-90`) - CPU, Memory, Storage limits\\n2. **`NetworkPolicy`** / `NetworkRule` (`types.go:102-110`) - Network access rules\\n3. **`LifecycleHook`** (`types.go:115-123`) - PreStart/PostStop callbacks\\n4. **`ContainerSpec`*...\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/results/runs/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z_logs/AR-002_ST-4.log:\n  Line 4: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775840252031,\"sessionID\":\"ses_287ad6a83ffeH4bz0BkZUU7UOn\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d7852a8cb0010st8s0ocIg55Mf\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d78529669001aXQCKQ5y7CK2rX\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_287ad6a83ffeH4bz0BkZUU7UOn\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"task\",\"callID\":\"toolu_a4cf7f12076e4db68da893ff\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"command\":\"Explore codebase for CRD patterns in agentcube project\",\"description\":\"Explore agentcube CRD patterns\",\"prompt\":\"Explore the agentcube project in /home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/openc